data.description: Warm & welcoming! Located in Tacoma's Waller district. This spacious modern farmhouse sits on a shy .75 acre corner lot w/ breathtaking views of Mt. Rainier. Home features a cover porch, spacious 2.5 car garage, 2 rooms, a bonus room on the lower level w/ a living, dining, family rm, & full bath. All Updated interior, beautiful white oak hardwoods throughout, a newly remodeled kitchen featuring shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, high-end stainless steel appliances & wood-burning fireplace. Upstairs includes a Large Primary suit w/ a fireplace, walk-in closet, update bath, & 2 extra rooms that can use as a bedroom, closet, or nursery. Prime location w/ easy access to shopping, amenities, schools, & freeways. Lots of Potential w/ this lot.
